snippet.title: [CQ X Re:ZERO] Collaboration Video
snippet.description:
Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Hasla-!

"Captain, you are the Hero of Hasla!
Let us start here. From square one... No, from zero!"

The CQ collaboration with popular light-novel-turned-into-an-anime series, Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- is here!☆
Say hello to 6 cute heroes from the Re:ZERO world! ♥

Silver-Haired Half-Elf, Emilia
Twin maids, Ram and Rem
Betty is quite cute, I suppose~ Beatrice
Blessed with the Divine Protection of Wind Indication, Crusch Karsten
Crusch Karsten's faithful knight, Ferris

To celebrate the CQ X Re:ZERO Collaboration, we'll have various events in game! We hope to see you all there 

■ CQ X Re:ZERO Collaboration PV Share Event!
Event Period: 01/16/19 ~ 01/30/19 PST
Winners announced: 2nd week of February
Steps to participate:
1) LIKE the PV!
2) SHARE the PV!
3) COMMENT below with a Re:ZERO Collaboration hero you're super excited about, and why! Don't forget to give us your IGN in your response!

You MUST complete all 3 steps to participate~
6 winners will be selected to receive a Re:ZERO Collaboration Hero of their choice, along with that Hero's SBW ♥

#cq #crusadersquest #collaboration #rezero
